snippet.title: DUSK - Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
New Blood presents DUSK - a retro FPS inspired by all your 90's favorites. 
Featuring a full single player campaign, endless survival mode and arena multiplayer. 
http://store.steampowered.com/app/519860
 
Music by Andrew Hulshult: https://youtu.be/eOAbv_Ey6eY

Join our Discord for a chance to win alpha keys! discord.gg/NewBlood

For more info visit NewBlood.games and follow @DuskGame and @TheNewBloods on Twitter.
